<div class="greeting">
  Hi {{firstName}},
</div>

<div class="alert alert-success">
  <strong>âœ“ Request Received</strong><br>
  We've received your maintenance request and will address it promptly.
</div>

<div class="info-box">
  <h3>Request Details</h3>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Request Number:</span>
    <span class="info-value"><strong>{{requestNumber}}</strong></span>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Category:</span>
    <span class="info-value">{{category}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Priority:</span>
    <span class="info-value">{{priority}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Location:</span>
    <span class="info-value">{{location}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Submitted:</span>
    <span class="info-value">{{submittedDate}}</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p><strong>Issue Description:</strong></p>
  <p style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px;">{{description}}</p>
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
  <ol>
    <li>Our team will review your request</li>
    <li>We'll schedule a visit if needed</li>
    <li>You'll receive updates via email and SMS</li>
    <li>We'll notify you when the work is complete</li>
  </ol>
</div>

{{#if isEmergency}}
<div class="alert alert-warning">
  <strong>Emergency Request</strong><br>
  This has been flagged as an emergency. Our team will respond within 4 hours.
</div>
{{/if}}

<a href="{{requestUrl}}" class="button">Track Request Status</a>

<div class="message">
  <p>You can track the progress of your request anytime in your tenant portal.</p>
  <p>Need urgent assistance? Call us at <strong>0700NYUMBA</strong></p>
</div>
